Raw: {
  "title": "The Collapse",
  "tempo_bpm": 120,
  "key": "E minor",
  "mood": "chaotic, intense",
  "lyrics": [
    {
      "text": "Shut up, George. This isn't about your ego or some pathetic attempt to 'add value' with a stupid kick drum.",
      "author": "singer"
    },
    {
      "text": "EGO? YOU CALL THAT KICK DRUM A 'PATETIC ATTEMPT' WHEN I’M THE ONLY ONE HERE WHO PLAYS LIKE THE WORLD’S ON FIRE AND NOT JUST BECAUSE SOMEONE TOOK OFF YOUR SUNGLASSES FOR TWO SECONDS?",
      "author": "drummer"
    },
    {
      "text": "NOISE?!",
      "author": "drummer"
    },
    {
      "text": "THIS ISN’T NOISE IT’S A DAMNED EARQUAKE.",
      "author": "drummer"
    },
    {
      "text": "YOU’RE JUST A POSER, JOHNATHAN. YOU THINK YOU CAN ‘CREATE AN EARTHQUAKE’ BY SMASHING DRUMS? GIVE ME SOMETHING REAL.",
      "author": "singer"
    },
    {
      "text": "REAL? THIS IS REAL!",
      "author": "drummer"
    },
    {
      "text": "PLAY YOUR ‘HYMN’ OR I’LL COUNT YOU OUT!",
      "author": "drummer"
    },
    {
      "text": "YOU WANT ‘NUMB AUTOMATONS’? THEN STAND HERE AND FEEL THIS.",
      "author": "bassist"
    },
    {
      "text": "YOU WANT ‘REAL’? THEN STAND HERE AND FEEL THIS.",
      "author": "bassist"
    },
    {
      "text": "ENOUGH POSING. THE BREAKDOWN’S NOT A DEBATE IT’S A COLLAPSE.",
      "author": "drummer"
    },
    {
      "text": "THIS’ NOT A SOLO BATTLE. THIS IS THE ROOM DYING AND WE’RE ALL CHOKING ON IT.",
      "author": "drummer"
    },
    {
      "text": "YOU WANT ‘NUMB AUTOMATONS’? THEN STAND HERE AND FEEL THIS.",
      "author": "bassist"
    },
    {
      "text": "YOU WANT ‘REAL’? THEN STAND HERE AND FEEL THIS.",
      "author": "bassist"
    },
    {
      "text": "SOMEONE PASS THE FIRE AXE BEFORE I SET MY OWN HEAD ON FLAMES.",
      "author": "bassist"
    },
    {
      "text": "I’LL LET THIS LINE MARRY THE BREAKDOWN… IF YOU ALL STOP WHINING FOR FIVE SECONDS.",
      "author": "drummer"
    },
    {
      "text": "YOU DON’T KNOW SILENCE. I’LL MAKE THAT SILENCE *SCREAM* BEFORE YOUR SOLO EVEN STARTS.",
      "author": "drummer"
    },
    {
      "text": "YOU WANT ‘REAL’? THEN STAND HERE AND FEEL THIS.",
      "author": "bassist"
    },
